text: All I Want (also known as Try Seventeen) is a 2002 coming-of-age comedy-drama movie directed by Jeffrey Porter and written by Charles Kephart. It stars Elijah Wood, Franka Potente and Mandy Moore. The movie premiered at the Toronto International Film Festival on September 10, 2002 and Palm Springs International Film Festival on January 12, 2003. == Other websites == * * Category:2002 romantic comedy movies Category:2000s coming-of-age movies Category:American romantic comedy movies Category:Coming-of-age romance movies Category:Coming-of-age comedy movies
